{
  "texts": [
    "And a few encouraging emojis might help!",
    "A Multimodal, Transpositional GrammarWe have been making the case that Generative AI creates meaning by paying statistical attention to the connections between words (tokens) to each other.",
    "Humans, by contrast, pay grammatical attention.",
    "The nouns and verbs people use embody a theory of the world where there are things and actions.",
    "Even when we don't call things out grammatically, our subconscious minds do."
  ]
}